apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: NetworkPolicy
metadata:
  name: allow-frontend-to-backend
spec:
  podSelector:
    matchLabels:
      app: backend      # ðŸ‘ˆ applies to backend pods
  policyTypes:
  - Ingress             # ðŸ‘ˆ controls incoming traffic
  ingress:
  - from:
    - podSelector:
        matchLabels:
          app: frontend  # ðŸ‘ˆ only allow pods with app=frontend to connect


This applies to the pod traffic
If network policy is applied on any pod all incoming/outgoing traffic is as per the network policy.
